{"tid":1257401,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"而家份工做得三個月就想轉工，點寫availability?","createTime":"2019-06-25T14:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T15:58:47.000Z","uid":123613,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0f210ccbc0932814b544a4b75a39f2e3c42cc671","tid":1257401,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"經濟有壓力加上做得唔開心，唔想祼辭，邊做邊搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果做過三個月，就要一個月通知期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題係而家咁個情況，寫cv又死，唔寫cv又死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫cv話自己返緊工，實俾人問點解做三個月就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔寫cv話自己冇返緊，hr一睇，點解要等成個月先返到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁個情況，大家照直講返緊工定冇返工?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返緊工，寫埋通知期<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇返工，賠錢即走"},{"pid":"cb2c02f4796df66995082ecfae974a55eaae5943","tid":1257401,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2d61b491b87925fcd3a274bea9877151c1bf21","tid":1257401,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"唔寫 做多半個月先搵 用半個月做通知期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58aa2067c1947c822b0df2c24b46e7aadabacce8","tid":1257401,"uid":2140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"我試過<br />\n你解釋到點解咁快走，加埋講到點解新果間唔會有呢啲問題就得<br />\n真係有實力既公司知道自己有能力留人，根本唔撚驚你走"},{"pid":"d175c05f5f82c6a5ceffb3d3f3e780bc054346f7","tid":1257401,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class